  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>POLICE FORCES FOUND AND RAIDED THE HOME OF THE FACELESS KILLER</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A serial killer known as the Faceless Killer has been terrorizing the people of Vipo. But finally, authorities have managed to locate his home, and a raid is ongoing. The story starts when John, one of the player characters, a reporter tries to capture exclusive footage of the events, live from the murderer's house. He has no idea what he got himself into.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082890/extras/7bd0e07325fb3dd45228694734957137.poster.avif?t=1735836570\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082890/extras/7bd0e07325fb3dd45228694734957137.webm?t=1735836570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082890/extras/7bd0e07325fb3dd45228694734957137.mp4?t=1735836570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PS1-Style graphics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Optional VHS shaders, imitating the style of 80s slasher movies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Narrative focused horror experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Logic puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scary atmosphere</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 player characters</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect VHS tapes to save your progress</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One playthrough takes around one hour</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 chapters, 4 endings</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082890/extras/d89e6170a25cd817758410ee1b786b2a.poster.avif?t=1735836570\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082890/extras/d89e6170a25cd817758410ee1b786b2a.webm?t=1735836570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082890/extras/d89e6170a25cd817758410ee1b786b2a.mp4?t=1735836570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082890/extras/4cf32066662c9bc256084df5661a6f5a.poster.avif?t=1735836570\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082890/extras/4cf32066662c9bc256084df5661a6f5a.webm?t=1735836570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082890/extras/4cf32066662c9bc256084df5661a6f5a.mp4?t=1735836570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
